Package nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.domain.Entity

Class Key

java.lang.Object
nz.ac.wgtn.swen225.lc.domain.Entity.Key
All Implemented Interfaces:
Entity
public class Key extends Object implements Entity
Represents a key entity in the game. A key can be used by the player to unlock doors of a specific colour. Each key has a unique colour associated with it, which determines the type of door it can unlock.
